{"tid":2067264,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"滙豐：因為客戶一直煩問黨安法立場，重申支持落實!","createTime":"2020-06-17T01:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T01:35:53.000Z","uid":14918,"like":12,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2e1eca42259824dd3c53d96fad46e45c83f377cd","tid":2067264,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T01:12:26.000Z","msg":"《經濟通通訊社１７日專訊》據彭博社引述滙豐（００００５）環球銀行及資本市場聯席主管Ｇｒｅｇ Ｇｕｙｅｔｔ向內部發放的備忘錄指，<span style=\"color: red;\">近日客戶幾乎在每一次會議都討論港區國安法話題，故重申支持落實港區國安法</span>，滙豐方面亦已證實備忘錄內容。  據備忘錄，滙豐強調自己在亞洲和西方之間扮演橋梁角色，因為香港是強大的市場，並擁有良好商業框架，同時相信中西方將繼續擁有深厚的經貿關係。<br />\n  滙豐又重申在一國兩制的原則下，尊重和支持所有穩定香港社會秩序、振興經濟繁榮發展的<br />\n法律。（ａｌ）（ｚｚ）"},{"pid":"8940ea6e3424333d3275fdb6717ba96583d31aef","tid":2067264,"uid":96909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T01:13:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26104d68d57b2a68f5d4036952e49858df2e42cf","tid":2067264,"uid":19557,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T01:13:42.000Z","msg":"好波 等你比人制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ebfb770a6d2c7e989a01eae3e66805cfd6fd87a","tid":2067264,"uid":343361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T01:13:59.000Z","msg":"借錢唔還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b488a2f54d235689528f5eee761ab97e3e6401d1","tid":2067264,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T01:14:08.000Z","msg":"CY?"},{"pid":"8549dbfcb4b7962be1a4a2b9af0b7c72d2e22b15","tid":2067264,"uid":259813,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T01:14:25.000Z","msg":"我地講咩都冇用，等美國同英國同你講"},{"pid":"b69eb1b2514a84cc9d22d001505c9f64e4b9d0ce","tid":2067264,"uid":32934,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T01:15:33.000Z","msg":"人地問你可以只係想CONFIRM下你係咪奶共, 奶就唔係度同你做生意廢事俾人制裁拎唔返D錢咋戇鳩."},{"pid":"34a8bf251169b0429791d6b03a0d89faaab7a235","tid"